eamUser</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/DoctorMcKay/node-steam-user\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">573</span></span></a> - A Node.js library for interacting with the Steam network via the the Steam client protocol.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/DoctorMcKay/node-steam-totp\">Steam TOTP</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/DoctorMcKay/node-steam-totp\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">192</span></span></a> - A Node.js library for generating Steam-style 2FA codes.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/liamcottle/valorant.js\">valorant.js</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/liamcottle/valorant.js\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;bor